{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/paperfaces/killing-joke-portrait/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"The Killing Joke","date":"2014-12-04T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"December 4th, 2014","date_from_now":"6 years ago","last_modified_at":"2017-09-07T20:16:56.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"3 years ago","path":"/paperfaces/killing-joke-portrait/","author":null,"excerpt":"PaperFaces portrait of the Joker from The Dark Knight drawn with Paper for iOS on an iPad.","tags":["portrait","illustration","Paper for iOS"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.3349514563106797,"src":"/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/fc20c/paperfaces-joker.jpg","srcSet":"/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/6e883/paperfaces-joker.jpg 275w,\n/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/a09ef/paperfaces-joker.jpg 550w,\n/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/fc20c/paperfaces-joker.jpg 1100w,\n/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/5d6ff/paperfaces-joker.jpg 1650w,\n/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/d2f4e/paperfaces-joker.jpg 2048w","sizes":"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/154cc80f9780839ab58ec34ffce2fe46/fc20c/paperfaces-joker.jpg","height":825,"width":1100}}},"toc":null,"comments":null,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":null},"id":"b4909a5a-6ada-5dc4-a92d-033b8bb878fd","html":"<p>While browsing through Mix looking for inspiration I came across a drawing shared by 赵 志欣 of Heath Ledger from <strong>The Dark Knight</strong>.</p>\n<p>I gave it a star to bookmark it for later, and then during the holiday weekend I got around to enhancing it some. I started by reworking the placement and proportions of the face and hand using an image of the Joker from one of the film’s posters.</p>\n<p>Using a soft and more loose approach, I painted with white to pull out highlights from the darker background. Followed by painting blue tones over the entire canvas to mimic the colors found in the poster. As always I finished up with pencil strokes to sharpen edges and correct any paint strokes that might have bleed more than I liked.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.9090909090909%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Work in process screenshot\"\n        title=\"Work in process screenshot\"\n        data-src=\"/static/ddcef6224376dcc497c00de7949df9fa/eacc7/paperfaces-joker-process-1-lg.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/ddcef6224376dcc497c00de7949df9fa/16841/paperfaces-joker-process-1-lg.jpg 275w,\n/static/ddcef6224376dcc497c00de7949df9fa/50c97/paperfaces-joker-process-1-lg.jpg 550w,\n/static/ddcef6224376dcc497c00de7949df9fa/eacc7/paperfaces-joker-process-1-lg.jpg 1100w,\n/static/ddcef6224376dcc497c00de7949df9fa/cc4ba/paperfaces-joker-process-1-lg.jpg 1650w,\n/static/ddcef6224376dcc497c00de7949df9fa/77bd5/paperfaces-joker-process-1-lg.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>Tools used:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://amzn.to/35tCkJW\">Pencil by FiftyThree</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://paper.bywetransfer.com/\">Paper for iOS</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"While browsing through Mix looking for inspiration I came across a drawing shared by 赵 志欣 of Heath Ledger from The Dark Knight. I gave it a…","timeToRead":1,"tableOfContents":""},"comments":{"edges":[]}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/paperfaces/vanessa-s-portrait/","title":"Tiger Style","categories":[